description: The time to reveal one’s true feelings is upon Asuna and Negi. But when Prince Charming himself appears by the name of one Fate Fidius Averruncus, whose happy ending will prevail? Will Asuna break with Negi forever, or will Negi turn out to be her white knight after all? Find out in the gripping final volume of Negima!? Neo!
name: Lucky No.7

description:
How many times in our lives , we spent hours trying to guess what might happen to us tomorrow?
How many times have we thought about what words to say at the  loved one or what justification to give to our employer for a mysterious absence?
And how many times we tried to make sense of events that have radically changed their lives ?
Nathan is trying to reflect on the future and try to figure out whether it is right to continue to working for the agency Alfa.
name: Il Mondo di Domani

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 25 - New X-Men (2004) # 44 - X-Men - Emperor Vulcan (2007) # 01,02

Mystery and intrigue, crime and punishment, uncovering the truth--all in a day’s work for the ace defense attorney Phoenix Wright and his beautiful assistant Maya Fey. Based on the hit game series, Ace Attorney brings new adventures to the games’ colorful cast. Can Nick successfully swing the gavel of justice or will he be crushed by the weight of incriminating evidence?
name: Objection to Injustice!

description:
The Third Call: A man who's mother recently passed away calls Black Jack's home office. As soon as the surgeon picks up the phone, the stranger on the other line goes into a long tirade about hospital conditions and the lack of care his mother's doctors were able to provide. He quickly turns to attack Black Jack's practices and his high fees, calling the rogue medic out for ignoring his medical roots to alienate the poor and challenged. And before he hangs up he informs BJ, that he has kidnapped Pinoko. He demands Black Jack lower his fees or else after three calls he will not only kill Pinoko he will kill everyone BJ saves.

Transcient Love: A young woman is dying from what has long been considered a terminal illness. With only about a month or so to live she shares her dying wish with her parents. Despite being bed-riden she wishes to someday marry. She wants to be a happy bride, and realize the joy of having someone love her eternally. Her father struck with grief, promises to marry his daughter to the first man who walks into her hospital room. That man is Black Jack, and his medical fees do not normally include fake marriage fees. This is going to be one costly marriage, however he cannot deny the fact her wish is essentially what is keeping her alive right now. If taking her hand will give her the strength to survive this procedure, it will have to considered part of the treatment.
name: Vol. 14

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 26 - New X-Men (2004) # 45 - X-Men - Emperor Vulcan (2007) # 03,04

Stand Alone Complex takes place in the year 2030, in the fictional Japanese city of New Port. The story follows the members of Public Security Section 9, a special-operations task-force made up of former military officers and police detectives. The manga presents individual cases that Section 9 investigates, along with an ongoing, more serious investigation into the serial killer and hacker known only as "The Laughing Man."

When a high-ranking government official is kidnapped, the Prime Minister must call in his top crime fighting force known as Section 9. Lead by the beautiful (and deadly) Major Kusanagi, the cybernetically enhanced squad must use all their skill to take down the kidnappers and rescue the hostages. But that’s only half of the mission; can Kusanagi and company find out who’s behind the kidnapping, and, more importantly, just what they’re after? Find out in this thrilling first volume of The Ghost in the Shell: Stand Alone Complex!

Chapter Titles

  • #001: Emergency Meeting
  • #002: Surrounded
  • #003: Move In
  • #004: Lauching Attack
  • #005: Search Initiated
  • #006: Loose Cannon
  • #007: Searching for Evidence
  • #008: Blind Spot
  • #009: Classified
  • #010: Imposter
  • #011: The Truth
name: Episode 1: Section 9

volume.name: Ghost in the Shell: Stand Alone Complex

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 27 - New X-Men (2004) # 46 - X-Men - Emperor Vulcan (2007) # 05 - X-Men (2004) # 207
Collects Ion: Guardian of the Universe issues 7-12

The planet is on the brink of destruction and Haru must finally face the evil Lucia once and for all. Haru’s only hope is to enter Endless and fight Lucia on his own turf, but even Haru can’t destroy Endless on his own. Only Elie’s Etherion is powerful enough to stop Endless and save the planet. Haru is perfectly willing to sacrifice his own life in order to conquer the forces of evil, but Elie refuses to unleash Etherion until Haru is out of harm’s way. The future of all humanity hangs in the balance and time is running out. Will Elie launch Etherion in time to save the human race? Find out in the final volume of Rave Master!

Triple sized volume containing volumes 33-35.
name: Vol. 33-35

description:
In the latest volume of Chi's Sweet Home, the titular kitten takes to the streets with unbridled curiosity. Exploring her new surroundings she encounters countless new friends, including another young feline named Cocchi. This new kitty comrade opens up a whole new world for our star. Prior to this encounter she had a mild awareness of what it was like to be a cat. To Chi, she was Chi and the Yamada's were her clan. But now with another one of her kind clearly there, she is more willing than ever to accept that a cat's world is one that she should be and will eventually be a part of. So while on a rare night excursion, our furry heroine reunites with an old friend and is introduced to a world where a whole community of cats of all shapes and sizes congregate in the twilight. This reunion with her mentor Blackie allows Chi to slowly move closer and closer to that long awaited reunion with her own cat family. Even if she is no longer searching for her own original home it is suddenly closer than it's ever been.

Chapter Titles

  • Homemade 93: a cat leaves her mark
  • Homemade 94: a cat is stopped
  • Homemade 95: a cat battles
  • Homemade 96: a cat appears
  • Homemade 97: a cat beckons
  • Homemade 98: a cat is satisfied
  • Homemade 99: a cat is pleased
  • Homemade 100: a cat celebrates
  • Homemade 101: a cat shares
  • Homemade 102: a cat is sucked
  • Homemade 103: a cat tosses
  • Homemade 104: a cat peeks
  • Homemade 105: a cat opens her heart
  • Homemade 106: a cat is copied
  • Homemade 107: a cat accepts
  • Homemade 108: a cat saunters
  • Homemade 109: a cat continues to saunter
  • Homemade 110: a cat steps forth
name: Volume 6

description:
Barbe-Rouge and "Le démon des Caraïbes" had originally been published in the first 40 issues of the French magazine Pilote beginning in 1959, before it was released as graphic novel in 1961.

The official English title is "The Broken Compass" although the original French title translates to "The Caribbean Demon".
name: Le démon des Caraïbes

Humans and technodroids fight  now united against a new , seemingly incontrovertible enemy, who 's objective is the annihilation of mankind and the advent of a superior race of machines . Opponents of a time  gather together to tackle this major new threat, while  Nemo and the Nautilus  are lost in the temporal  maelstrom ...
name: La grande minaccia

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 34 - X-Force - Ain't No Dog (2008) -Young X-Men (2008) # 06 - Astonishing X-Men - Ghost Boxes (2008) # 01

The Nautilus, after the bloody war that has seen the newly allied humans and technodroids on the one hand contrasting the silent "Greys" on the other, is about to go through a crack in space-time from which a mysterious radiopulse comes out. Under the command of the ship, after the death of Nemo (whose mind has been downloaded into the onboard computer), Artisia launches herself into the dimensional crack to shed light on the strange phenomenon, and finds herself in a parallel solar system where a war is going on between a demon Empress and a rebel human alliance , supported by an ancient guild of telepath women.
name: Le due nemiche

description: Collects : X-Factor : Layla Miller (2008) - X-Force (2008) # 07 - Young X-Men (2008) # 07 - Astonishing X-Men : Ghost Boxes (2008) 02

Megan Ray , a brilliant female manager , hides a secret . Why somebody is fiercely hunting her?  But most of all : who hides under the command of the organization known as the " Laboratory" ? Nathan and Branko try to shed light on these questions in a survey that will take them back to the events of the mutate people.
name: Doppia Identità

Solomon Darver has now assumed the full control of the Alpha Agency: the relationship with the agents seem to have stabilized and the relations between the Agency and the new city administration are excellent. But when everything seems to be going well, suddenly something disturbs his life. He receives an anonymous letter with  the details of a numbered account that "can not exist", that  forced  Darver to reveals sensational truth to his agents ...
name: Chi è Solomon Darver?

Nathan Never again cross his path with that of Salomon Wolfach , the protagonist of " Thor 14" ( Nathan Never n. 57) .
While the Agency Alfa is in charge of security of an important conference between the Terran Confederation and the orbital colonies , Nathan comes to discover that someone of the participants  has a terrible weapon in his hand : the deadly -vampire bullets with an  automatic search of the target created in a secret military facility.
name: Corsa Contro la Morte

description: Someone has awakened, from his sleep in Arctic , the terrible weapon known as  Thor 14.  Nathan Never will join forces with  Solomon Wolfach in a desperate  mission.
name: Il risveglio di Thor 14

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 49 - Astonishing X-Men (2004) # 35 - New Mutants (2009) # 05 - X-Force (2008) # 20

A terrible attack , triggers panic in the city and beyond its borders .

Diplomacy is helpless, a diabolical plan begins to take shape , and the world in short time is on the verge of war.

Nathan Never , his the first line with any agents of the Alpha Agency , they will dissolve the complicated situation ...

This is the start of an adventure whose consequences will grow throughout the years to come!
name: Venti Di Guerra

description: Collects : X-Factor (2006) # 50 - New Mutants (2009) # 06 - X-Force (2008) # 21- X-Necrosha - The Gathering (2010)
name: X-Necrosha parte 2 di 9

description: The Butcher has his final showdown with Corvus...50,000 feet in the air, leaving one victor. And one corpse. Green Arrow guest-stars.
The Butcher has his final showdown with Corvus...50,000 feet in the air, leaving one victor. And one corpse. Green Arrow guest-stars.
The Butcher's unrelenting fury begins to take its toll on the corporation as they begin to turn on their own...only to be hit again by John and his martial arts master.
The Butcher has a date with destiny as his quest to avenge the death of his parents takes him to San Francisco...and a deadly encounter.

A new menace from the Canadian Rockies has reared its head, threatening everything and everybody that crosses its path. It's a menace so powerful, so evil, that only the toughest, most ruthless of super-heroes can ever hope to defeat it. That hero is THE BUTCHER. The Butcher is the newest hero in the DC Universe...and the most mysterious. Who is he? Where did he come from? There are answers to those questions...but don't expect them to come easily. Because nothing is ever easy for the Butcher.
name: Present

description:
Finally , the plan of Skotos it's clear ... clear and monstrous!

The crazy preacher, in fact, wants to upset the whole balance of the planet's climate because, from its ruins , can be born a Terrible new world .

A world in which there is no place for the mutants of Hell's Island , against which he has unleashed hordes of his tecnodroidi .

Nathan , Branko , Legs and May break into his palace to stop him , but the large rooms are empty.

Aristotele Skotos was able to take refuge in an undisclosed location from which to begin his plan of Revelation .

But Skotos will have to deal with an unexpected Neos, the technodroid boy, who is not as controllable as the preacher hopes...
name: L'Alba Dell'Apocalisse

description:
The " Great Flood " triggered by the ionic satellites of mad preacher Aristotele Skotos , is now producing its devastating effects on the entire planet , and nothing seems to could stop it .

Tremendous rains afflict the earth, terrible tsunamis shakes the abysses and hitting the coasts ,whole atolls in a short span of time are swallowed by the boiling sea.

Nathan and his companions haven't yet managed to find the hideout of Skotos but when all seems irremediably lost , a completely unexpected help will give to Nathan and his companions a hope of victory.
name: Aristotele Skotos

description:
During the difficult political situation between the Earth and the orbiting stations , Nathan Never was hired as a bodyguard and "coach " of an important diplomat, the senator from Talia , Ramon Echavarretía .

He has decided , for reasons of political opportunism , to take part in a tournament of Jeet Kune Doo , the martial art where Nathan excels .

Someone , however , take the opportunity to try to kill the Senator ...
name: Shaolin

description: When a mail cart containing a special package is hijacked by thieves, Po takes action! Determined to recover the package, Po’s search leads to a strange city, but will he be able to find the thieves? Or his way back home? And what is so special about that package anyway?
name: Special Delivery; Pong

description: "Genesis" Part One: You know the hero, you know the villain, but you haven't seen anything like this! Celebrate Sonic's 20th anniversary! It's a brand new adventure as Sonic the Hedgehog investigates the disappearance of many woodland creatures, and discovers the man behind it all! It's an all-new beginning!
name: Genesis Part One: In the Beginning...

description: LAST ISSUE! Coheed and Cambria frontman Claudio Sanchez and comics legend Peter David bring you the epic conclusion to the “Silent Earth” saga! Claudio’s ship of misfit warriors joins Inferno and his rebel army, taking the fight directly to Wilhelm Ryan and House Atlantic. It’s a battle for the ages as Claudio’s survival hinges on whether The Crowing was really his destiny…or just a myth.

volume.name: The Amory Wars: In Keeping Secrets of Silent Earth: 3

description: Wilson Fisk is a bodyguard for mob boss Don Rigoletto, but he has his eyes on a much bigger prize, and he's gonna use Frank Castle to help him realize his dreams. It's the biggest story in MAX history, as we witness the birth of the greatest villain the Punisher has ever faced.
name: Kingpin

description: THE ROAD TO “CHAOS” ENDS HERE! With his army assembled, Galvatron is ready to take the Heart of Darkness back to Cybertron. But first, he must now face down the ultimate threat, a force of unimaginable power and overwhelming darkness. Will Galvatron stand strong or will he bend to the will of inescapable evil? HoD leads directly into “CHAOS”—the first-ever TRANSFORMERS event book from IDW!

They say he's the deadliest assassin the world has ever known. They say that once he sets his sights on someone, he never misses, no matter what he has to go through to get them. Though his methods may seem unorthodox, even insane, they say he's never failed to kill a single target.

No one knows where he comes from or why he does it. No one knows his name. They all just call him Bullseye. And now he's come to New York City, with his sights set on Frank Castle. Let the hunt begin. If you thought our new MAX version of Kingpin was intense, you ain't seen nothing yet.
name: Bullseye

description: An earth-shattering volume collecting stories from Whiz Comics #2,Captain Marvel Adventures #1,137,148, Marvel Family #21, 85, Shazam! #1, 14, DC Comics Presents Annual #3, Superman #276, L.E.G.I.O.N. '91 #31, Power of SHAZAM! #33 and Adventures in the DC Universe #5.
name: TPB

volume.name: Shazam: The Greatest Stories Ever Told

description:
ALL-NEW FROM ROBERT KIRKMAN & JASON HOWARD!

Super Dinosaur and Derek Dynamo protect the world from the denizens of Inner Earth! Meanwhile, Max Maximus’ master plan finally begins to take shape... and it’s BIGGER than anything Super Dinosaur and Derek have faced thus far! This issue can’t be missed, just like every issue of SUPER DINOSAUR!

name: Il re di Darkwood
